# Buyma Insider

## SETUP

```
# Start rethinkdb with docker
docker run  --name rethinkdb -p 8080:8080 -p 28015:28015 --rm greyarch/rethinkdb

# Launching unicorn locally
ENVIRONMENT=development be unicorn -c config/unicorn.rb -E $ENVIRONMENT -d

# Launching pry
ENVIRONMENT=development be pry -Iapp:config:db -r 'buyma_insider'
```

## NOTE

- Use be ruby to run patches instead of pry, pry screws up sometimes the format
